text: Tinadendron noumeanum is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to New Caledonia. ==References== * Jaffré, T. et al. 1998. Guettarda noumeana. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 21 August 2007.
